Class MockedPropertyPolygon

java.lang.Object
Models.PropertyPolygon
Utils.Mocks.MockedPropertyPolygon
public class MockedPropertyPolygon extends PropertyPolygon
The MockedPropertyPolygon class is a mock implementation of the PropertyPolygon class. It is used for testing purposes to simulate a property polygon with predefined attributes.
